(GPU Build Behavior) Tj
T*
(- OpenCL binary build is attempted on all supported hosts.) Tj
T*
(- CUDA binary build is attempted only when:) Tj
T*
(- OS supports CUDA build path, and) Tj
T*
(- nvcc is present.) Tj
T*
(- On macOS, CUDA output is expected to be skipped.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Legacy Paths) Tj
T*
(Legacy source-tree binary mirrors are disabled. Runtime and pinning use only Binaries/.) Tj
T*
() Tj
